<br>
I'd like it noted i'm posting here cuz im afraid this might turn into some sort of flame, i can never tell, I've seen flames from more innocent things.<br>
<br>
I'm doing a school report called the Senior Search.  We have to pick a topic we are interested in, and write a massive report about it.  So, I'm doing mine on whether or not online games are truely addictive.  I figured id ask you guys, since most of you have no doubt been playing longer then me, and have interesting opinions <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Waiting (almost with dread) to see what kind of reception this will get.<br>
<br>
